data.description: Welcome to the desirable and sought out community Preserve at Tradition. This 4 bedrooms and 2 baths charming single-family property constructed in 2021, boast a generously spacious open floor concept that creates an inviting environment, perfect for hosting gatherings. The master suite serves as a private oasis, featuring an appointed spacious en-suite bathroom. The additional bedrooms are generously sized and versatile. The community itself offers a range of amenities, including a dog park, playground, and  resort style pool creating an ideal setting for both relaxation and recreation. Easy access to the highway and conveniently located near shopping, dining and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to call this your home.
